    <!-- Services -->
    <section id="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h3 class="pb-4">What we do</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <article>
              <p class="dropcap">We build websites. From simple landing pages or product sites to blogs 
                and online stores, we build responsive designs using grid based approaches and frameworks.
                Our designs look great on mobile while also scaling gracefully to desktop dimensions. 
                Intuitive content management systems are utilized, allowing you to easily update and manage your site.
              </p>
              <p>Already have a site? We can refresh or entirely reboot your online identity with a comprehensive 
                overhaul. Have more complex needs? CMS migrations, bespoke dashboards to manage and visualize your
                business data, custom administrative portals for your employees and customers, or custom programming 
                to connect a legacy system or data source to the web are all possibilities.
              </p>
              <p>Straightforward contracts with fixed, understandable costs. Deliverables on-time and on-budget.
              </p>
              <p><a class="js-scroll-trigger" href="#contact">Engage</a> us for a one off project or retain us for affordable ongoing support and
                design work for existing websites.
             </p>
           </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h3 class="pb-4">Our Process</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row services">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-6 ml-auto">
                <div class="pb-4 pr-4">
                  <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Strategy</h4>
                  <p>
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-2x fa-pull-left mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-tertiary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  We start with a discussion. What are your goals? What message do you want to communicate?
                  Your website is the primary platform for engaging and retaining your audience.
                  It needs to communicate a coherent brand and identity that reflects your organization’s 
                  values and leaves a strong positive impression on the first visit.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6 mr-auto">
                <div class="pb-4 pr-4">
                  <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Design</h4>
                  <p>
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-2x fa-pull-left mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-tertiary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-rocket fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  We prototype your site’s look and feel: UX, typography, color palette.
                  We define functional requirements, site organization and navigation.
                  Your overall branding can be created by us or we can integrate your established
                  branding into a new design.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row bottom-line">
              <div class="col-lg-6 ml-auto">
                <div class="pb-4 pr-4">
                  <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Development</h4>
                  <p>
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-2x fa-pull-left mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-tertiary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-code fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  Next we choose appropriate frameworks and a CMS and begin the process of translating
                  the prototype into code to fully realize the design. Our code is prioritized for
                  accessibility, performance, and responsiveness.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6 mr-auto">
                <div class="pb-4 pr-4">
                  <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Deployment</h4>
                  <p>
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-2x fa-pull-left mr-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-tertiary"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-server fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  We deliver final assets and code for integration into the server setup of your choice 
                  or we can deploy and manage your website for you, handling all the nitty-gritty IT 
                  details so you don’t have to.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <h3 class="pb-4">Specialities</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Design</h4>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li>Illustration</li>
          <li>Motion Graphics</li>
          <li>Photographic and<br>
            Video Content Creation</li>
          <li>Copywriting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Front-End</h4>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li>HTML, CSS, JS</li>
          <li>CMS (Squarespace, Wordpress)</li>
          <li>Frameworks (Bootstrap, jQuery)</li>
          <li>Performance</li>
          <li>Accessibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h4 class="pt-4 mb-4 text-muted">Server-Side</h4>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li>Web, Mail, Database hosting</li>
          <li>Domain Name Services</li>
          <li>Server optimization, scaling & CDNs</li>
          <li>Cloud Services<br>
            (Digital Ocean, Linode, AWS, Netlify)</li>
          <li>Database design</li>
          <li>Site Migrations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
